flowchart TD
  A[User Opens App] --> B{Authenticated?}
  B -- No --> C[Login or Register]
  C --> D[Issue JWT Access + Refresh Tokens]
  D --> E[Load Dashboard]
  B -- Yes --> E

  E --> F{Choose Feature}
  F --> G[Chat with RAG]
  F --> H[Upload Documents]
  F --> I[View Analytics]
  F --> J[Manage Users - Admin]

  H --> K[Parse Document]
  K --> L[Chunk + Embed]
  L --> M[Store Vectors in Qdrant]
  M --> N[Store Metadata in PostgreSQL]

  G --> O[Retrieve Top-K Context]
  O --> P[Generate LLM Response]
  P --> Q[Return Answer + Sources]

  I --> R[Aggregate Metrics]
  J --> S[Update Roles / Status]
  Q --> T[Persist Session and Messages]
